    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just keep thinking about how much easier it would be if the noise would just stop. if i didn't have to wake up and face the person i've become. it feels like the world has already moved on and decided i don't exist anymore. why does it even matter to keep fighting for a life that’s already over?",
